00:25:43.279 --> 00:25:46.360
There's no communion between light and darkness.

00:25:46.360 --> 00:25:49.600
And what I was is not what I am.

00:25:49.600 --> 00:25:50.839
Praise God for that.

00:25:51.839 --> 00:25:56.080
I'm so glad that I'm not what I used to be, amen?

00:25:56.080 --> 00:25:57.080
